o Branco]], [[Cerro Largo Department|Cerro Largo]] * SURV (RVY) – [[Rivera International Airport|Pte. Gral. Óscar D. Gestido International Airport]] – [[Rivera]], [[Rivera Department|Rivera]] * SUSO (STY) – [[Nueva Hesperides International Airport|Nueva Hespérides International Airport]] – [[Salto, Uruguay|Salto]], [[Salto Department|Salto]] * SUTB (TAW) – [[Tacuarembó Airport]] – [[Tacuarembó]], [[Tacuarembó Department|Tacuarembó]] * SUTR (TYT) – [[Treinta y Tres Airport]] – [[Treinta y Tres]], [[Treinta y Tres Department|Treinta y Tres]] * SUVO (VCH) – [[Vichadero Airport]] – [[Vichadero]], [[Rivera Department|Rivera]]
