ela)|Bolívar]] * SVSO (STD) – [[Mayor Buenaventura Vivas Airport]] – [[Santo Domingo, Táchira|Santo Domingo]] * SVSP (SNF) – [[Sub Teniente Nestor Arias Airport]] – [[San Felipe, Yaracuy]] * SVSR (SFD) – [[Las Flecheras Airport]] – [[San Fernando de Apure]], [[Apure State|Apure]] * SVST (SOM) – [[San Tomé Airport]] – [[San Tomé, Venezuela|San Tomé]] * SVSZ (STB) – [[Miguel Urdaneta Fernández Airport]] – [[Santa Bárbara del Zulia]] * SVTC (TUV) – [[San Rafael Airport (Venezuela)|San Rafael Airport]] – [[Tucupita]], [[Delta Amacuro State|Delta Amacuro]] * SVTM (TMO) – [[Tumeremo Airport]] – [[Tumeremo]] * SVUM (URM) – [[Uriman Airport]] – [[Bolívar State (Venezuela)|Bolívar]] * SVVA (VLN) – [[Arturo Michelena International Airport]] – [[Valencia, Carabobo]] * SVVG (VIG) – [[Juan Pablo Pérez Alfonzo Airport]] – [[El Vigia]] * SVVL (VLV) – [[Dr. Antonio Nicolás Briceno Airport]] – [[Valera]], [[Trujillo State|Trujillo]]
