[[File:Countries by highest point map.PNG|thumb|Map of countries coloured according to their highest point]]
The following sortable table lists '''land surface elevation extremes by country'''.

[[Elevation|Topographic elevation]] is the vertical distance above the reference [[geoid]], a mathematical model of the Earth's [[sea level]] as an [[equipotential]] [[Gravity|gravitational]] surface.

